                "imgDesc": "<p>In some places, you will find this mysterious combo of mechanisms: the Discharge Stone and the Cumulation Stone. The former shoots a harmless electric current at characters and monsters <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 225, 75)\">affected by Electro</span> while the latter absorbs the electrical energy from the Discharge Stone. Sometimes you will also find Relay Stones, which conduct the current released by Discharge Stones.</p>",
